  instructionPanel: {fileID: 1689754333}
  instructionSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 168f6520baddff42692d29333c4f75c4, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Eliminate All Threats\n\nThe Engineering Sector is patrolled by Grunt
      and Berserker units. Berserkers are heavily armored and move fast \u2014 keep
      your distance. Use your Rifle for long range and switch to Pistol to conserve
      ammo. Clear all enemies before proceeding."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8d89779f8d01fb32b927e1687ff7c157, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Destroy Crates for Supplies\n\nWooden crates are scattered across
      the sector. Shoot them to break them open \u2014 they may drop Ammo or Health
      Packs. Low on ammo? Search every room before engaging enemies. Always check
      corners and side corridors for hidden crates."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 30e6edc762aa2d4cba5f740dd15272bf, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Use Explosive Barrels\n\nRed barrels found throughout the sector are
      highly explosive. Shoot a barrel near a group of enemies to deal massive area
      damage. Stay back \u2014 the explosion will damage you too if you are too close.
      Use them to your advantage when outnumbered."
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4d898e031c77a0be19e41fe9ff974880, type: 3}
    bodyText: 'Restore Power to the Locked Room


      Two Power Cells are hidden
      somewhere in the sector. Collect both Power Cells to restore power to the locked
      door. Walk over a Power Cell to collect it automatically. The door will only
      open once both cells have been found.'
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c02e6047035f4d52c80b7dac6cb6a180, type: 3}
    bodyText: 'Find the Access Key


      Once the locked room is open, locate the
      Access Key inside. Walk over it to collect it automatically. Head to the Exit
      Door and press [E] to proceed to the next stage of the mission.'
  slideImage: {fileID: 1134806202}
  slideBodyText: {fileID: 92091610}
  slideCounterText: {fileID: 2085516441}
  slideNextButton: {fileID: 2099289413}
  slidePrevButton: {fileID: 1675951320}
